picon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1713861582816"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>SkinTalks</p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" id="r-1711632530427" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1711632530427" style="float: none; margin: auto; display: block;" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_col-lg-12 gf_column" id="c-1596783587877" data-id="1596783587877"><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1711632530393" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1711632530393"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1696332878138" data-id="1696332878138"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1711632530517" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1711632530517"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 670px !important; height: 156.734px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 335px 78.3672px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 670px !important; height: 156.734px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="65" height="21" style="display: none; top: 68px !important; left: 44px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-justify-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-679023" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p>Hey there, SkinTalks readers! As we embrace winter, it's the perfect time to show your skin some extra love. <span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);">Just as we snuggle up in cozy blankets and enjoy hot cocoa, our skin deserves a bit of pampering too.</span></p><p><br></p><p>The winter weather, with its chilly air and indoor heating, can be a bit challenging for our skin. But fear not! We've got your back with a set of winter skincare tips that will not only keep your skin in top-notch condition, but are also delightfully easy to incorporate into your routine.</p><p><br></p><p>Let's embark on a journey through the ultimate winter skincare routine, designed to combat the effects of the cold and keep your skin radiant.<span style="background-color: rgba(183, 227, 255, 0.25);"> From hydrating cleansers to nourishing <a href="https://www.koreanskincare.co.uk/collections/moisturisers" class="">moisturisers</a>, we've curated a collection of winter skincare products that are sure to become your seasonal favorites.</span></p><p><br></p><p>So, grab your favorite mug, fill it with your go-to winter beverage, and let's toast to a season of glowing skin and warmth, all courtesy of our carefully selected winter skincare essentials. Get ready to pamper your skin, and let the beauty of winter radiate not just around you, but also through you!&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Here are the best Korean Skincare tips for winter.</p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1711632530449" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1711632530449"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1711632530391" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1711632530391"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 25px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 12.5px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 26px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-5051" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><b>Switch out your cleanser</b></h2></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1711632530414" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1711632530414" data-layout-lg="12" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12" style=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653642484175" data-id="1653642484175"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1711632530451" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1711632530451"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 670px !important; height: 156.734px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 335px 78.3672px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 670px !important; height: 156.734px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="65" height="21" style="display: none; top: 68px !important; left: 44px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-justify-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-679023" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p>As winter sets in, our skin often becomes a battleground with the effect of cold weather. It faces off against the elements that threaten to rob it of precious moisture. Harsh cleansers are a no-go during this time of year. Because they may strip away natural oils and leave our skin feeling parched from the inside out.</p><p><br></p><p>Here's the winter skincare wisdom: <span style="background-color: rgba(183, 227, 255, 0.25);">steer clear of products that contain ingredients like fragrances, additives, salicylic acid, and charcoal.</span> These can be your skin's worst enemy during the chilly months. Instead, embrace the gentle touch of lotions, gels, or low-foam cleansers. But that's not all; turn the label detective mode on, and look for cleansers that boast hydrating heroes like hyaluronic acid, chamomile, ceramides, and glycerin.</p><p><br></p><p><span style="background-color: rgba(183, 227, 255, 0.25);">By making small changes to your skincare routine, you can keep your skin glowing and moisturised during harsh winter weather.</span> After all, who doesn't want to face the frosty world with a glowing, confident complexion?</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Our top moisturising cleansers for winter are:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1711632530510" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1711632530510" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653642484175" data-id="1653642484175"><div data-label="Product" data-key="product" data-atomgroup="product" id="m-1711632530473" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-product" data-ver="3.1" data-id="1711632530473" data-assigned-ver="4" style="min-height: auto;"><div class="module" data-variant="auto" style="" data-current-variant="39724076728449"><product-form c