it like giving our skin an extra cozy layer of protection against the chilly winds and dry air.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Look for stuff with shea butter and hyaluronic acid – they're like superheroes for keeping our skin all plump and happy. Oh, and don't forget those elbows and hands, they need some extra love too. So, let's embrace the thicker moisturiser vibe this winter and keep our skin feeling all kinds of amazing!</p><p></p><p><br><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit; color: rgb(17, 17, 18); font-weight: bold;">Here's why it's beneficial:</span><br><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: rgba(168, 220, 255, 0.25);">Enhanced Protection: </span>Thicker moisturisers create a strong barrier, shielding your skin from harsh winter elements like cold winds and low humidity, reducing water loss.</span><br><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: rgba(168, 220, 255, 0.25);">Deeper Hydration:</span> They contain more emollient ingredients like shea and cocoa butter for intense, long-lasting hydration.</span><br><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: rgba(168, 220, 255, 0.25);">Preventing Moisture Loss:</span> Thicker moisturisers protect against increased water loss, often seen in winter, due to compromised skin barriers.</span><br><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: rgba(168, 220, 255, 0.25);">Soothing:</span> Many thick moisturisers include soothing ingredients to relieve dryness, redness, and sensitivity.</span><br><br><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><span style="background-color: rgba(168, 220, 255, 0.25);">Long-Lasting:</span> Their dense texture provides prolonged hydration, reducing the need for frequent reapplication, ideal for busy winter days</span><br><br><strong style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">Our winter moisturiser favorites are:&nbsp;</strong><br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1711632530479" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1711632530479" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653642484175" data-id="1653642484175"><div data-label="Product" data-key="product" data-atomgroup="product" id="m-1711632530501" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-product" data-ver="3.1" data-id="1711632530501" data-assigned-ver="4" style="min-height: auto;"><div class="module" data-variant="auto" style="" data-current-variant="39724093702273"><product-form class="product-form">{% assign product = all_products['rnw-der-special-ceramide-cream'] %}{% unless product.empty?  %}{% form 'product', product, id: "", class: "AddToCartForm ", data-productid: product.id %}<input name="id" type="hidden" value="{{product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id}}" data-productid="{{product.id}}"><div data-index="1" class="item-content"><div class="module-wrap" id="m-1711632530501-0" data-id="1711632530501-0" data-label="(P) Image"><div class="module gf_module-center gf_module-center-lg gf_module--md gf_module--sm gf_module--xs" data-effect="default" data-pid="{{product.id}}" data-image-type="variant" data-default-variant="{{defaultVariant}}" data-select-text="{{selectText}}" data-zoom-level="1.2" data-ori-size="1024x